metadata.name: Liz OGarvey-Multiphasic Revolutionaries
metadata.description:
Native species of feminist, punk, queer, digital disobedients inhabiting the cracks and hollows, spotted in the wild, turning things inside out.

Reject erasure of our disruptors, their actions, art, history & entire culture of disruption.

Liz O’Garvey Bio:
As a receptive artist who loses themselves in fascination and passion, I turn things inside out and work miracles with scraps and remains, during our current asymmetric era.

MA Visual Arts-Film, Video, Photography & Communication as a social science, Regents Scholarship, Summa cum Laude
MFA Directing for Film & Theatre, Jacob K. Javits Fellowship
